WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:02.667
Well, good evening, everybody.

00:00:02.667 --> 00:00:05.760
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:11.580
We'll go over some of the things the Lord showed us last Friday before I took my break.

00:00:12.280 --> 00:00:14.1000
We're backing up for another week of prayer.

00:00:15.660 --> 00:00:20.098
Thank you for joining me, and we'll see what the Lord has for us tonight.

00:00:20.809 --> 00:00:22.720
All glory to Jesus.

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:24.519
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

00:00:25.119 --> 00:00:29.413
There's a lot happening in the news, isn't there?

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:42.560
But tonight's video is 'The Valley of Decision' for what I'm praying over for President Trump concerning his major decisions that he's going to make.

00:00:42.560 --> 00:00:46.520
The Lord gave me this in prayer, and I'm just going to jump right into it.

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:48.468
I just felt the unction of the Holy Ghost.

00:00:48.468 --> 00:00:51.759
Thank you, Holy Spirit.

00:00:53.199 --> 00:00:57.600
When I was in prayer yesterday, I got caught up in the Spirit.

00:00:57.600 --> 00:01:06.466
Over the next two weeks—I want you to hear this very carefully—major decisions will be made concerning Iran and Pakistan.

00:01:14.159 --> 00:01:19.840
Major disruptions are about to erupt in Pakistan.

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:22.011
I saw Pakistan very clearly.

00:01:22.011 --> 00:01:24.640
The Lord said there are things about to take place.

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:27.080
Now, you might say, 'Well, Brandon, when is that going to take place?

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:31.813
' I don't know; I see in part, but I saw Pakistan and Iran highlighted.

00:01:34.845 --> 00:01:49.680
As I saw this major thing about to happen in Iran, I heard anti-Semitism will be at an all-time high in the days ahead.

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:52.720
I saw New York City again.

00:01:52.720 --> 00:02:09.759
I saw the Jewish community in New York City and in other parts of the United States, as well as Jewish communities in other nations, under great persecution.

00:02:10.171 --> 00:02:19.280
I saw great anti-Semitism coming at an all-time high in the days ahead concerning the Jewish people.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:25.360
I saw great protests, and I saw that some of them were in danger.

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:31.200
When I was shown this, I saw people fleeing to Israel.

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:39.440
They were uprooting their families in these major cities and they said, 'We've had enough.

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:44.959
' They were getting their things and moving to Israel.

00:02:44.959 --> 00:02:46.960
I thought that was interesting.

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:51.314
I told Diana, 'Would you look that up, if what we're looking at is biblical?

00:02:51.314 --> 00:02:59.760
' She found scriptures about how God would bring the people back together after they were scattered in the end times.

00:03:03.707 --> 00:03:06.773
Like I said, I'm not a Bible scholar when it comes to stuff like this.

00:03:07.146 --> 00:03:12.376
When I'm looking in the spirit and the Lord is showing me things, I thought it was interesting.

00:03:12.376 --> 00:03:15.226
He said He was bringing His people home.

00:03:15.226 --> 00:03:18.023
He was bringing the Jewish people home.

00:03:18.411 --> 00:03:27.320
I saw the Jews going to Israel in mass numbers from persecution that will arise in the days ahead.

00:03:27.690 --> 00:03:35.120
They were all starting to come back to Jerusalem.

00:03:35.350 --> 00:03:40.720
I thought that was interesting on a greater scale in the days ahead.

00:03:46.826 --> 00:03:57.289
I saw fires all over with great protests in New York City.

00:03:57.289 --> 00:04:06.879
I saw the forty-first floor of a major building in New York City on fire again.

00:04:06.879 --> 00:04:14.760
I saw a lot of fires in buildings and rioting coming to New York in the days ahead.

00:04:15.010 --> 00:04:24.320
I thought that was interesting because He keeps showing me this over and over again concerning New York.

00:04:24.320 --> 00:04:36.950
He was upset again when I was praying in the spirit about the new mayor of New York and the decisions that are already being made.

00:04:37.448 --> 00:04:39.400
So we saw that.

00:04:39.400 --> 00:04:45.520
Now, I will go over what the Lord showed us Friday.

00:04:46.130 --> 00:05:05.972
I saw young men being paid off by the drug cartel in Venezuela trying to raise up an army against our troops that have been on the ground in Venezuela, but it was toward Brazil.

00:05:05.972 --> 00:05:22.560
I saw Cuba devising a plan on how to create civil unrest in Venezuela and Colombia.

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:31.567
I saw the cartel.

00:05:31.567 --> 00:05:46.480
I saw great operations of cocaine distribution plants—huge operations full of people who looked strung out and broken.

00:05:51.840 --> 00:06:02.827
I saw ten buildings that looked like metal buildings with waves, like wavy tin that you put on a chicken coop, a pig pen, or a barn.

00:06:12.011 --> 00:06:12.206
It was designed with metal on the outside, like stucco, but it was rusty.

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:16.183
It looked like it was rusty and falling apart.

00:06:16.183 --> 00:06:18.560
There were white stains on the buildings.

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:25.428
There was rust, and I could see where the nail holes were with rust coming down the sides of the buildings.

00:06:25.428 --> 00:06:29.759
I could see the roof, but they were manufacturing cocaine and drugs in them.

00:06:32.017 --> 00:06:38.983
It was all in Colombia on the border, and I saw major trafficking of drugs in those areas.

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:52.479
As I was looking into this, I saw highways that looked like veins spread out all over Europe, Africa, America, and Asia.

00:06:52.861 --> 00:07:00.520
I saw the Panama Canal, and they were taking the drugs and distributing them into Asia.

00:07:10.799 --> 00:07:11.119
I saw Cuba at high alert under great pressure.

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:21.587
I saw their president inside of a mountain.

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:51.680
He was in a bunker in the mountain, hiding out, afraid of the United States coming in and invading again like they did with Venezuela.

00:07:51.884 --> 00:07:52.702
He was lying low.

00:07:52.702 --> 00:07:56.759
He was in the ground similar to Saddam.

00:07:57.629 --> 00:08:01.580
He was hiding in that bunker, but this man was hiding.

00:08:01.580 --> 00:08:05.533
He's trying to be cocky because he thinks he's protected by the mountain.

00:08:05.787 --> 00:08:11.539
It would take something like a bunker buster to get him because there was only one way in and one way out.

00:08:11.879 --> 00:08:18.144
I could see these men with berets on their heads—some were African-American—standing at the entrance of this vault.

00:08:21.260 --> 00:08:30.091
It looked like a massive metal structure with a huge door, like something out of Doomsday Preppers.

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:41.668
I could see him again devising a plan to raise up soldiers to try to create havoc in Venezuela in the days ahead.

00:08:43.839 --> 00:08:51.040
How do we bring civil unrest and how do we destroy the oil wells they're after?

00:08:51.653 --> 00:09:02.809
I saw huge white containers made to hold oil, and they were targeting them.

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:11.954
Some were on the water and some were inland, but I could see these containers full of oil and they were targeting them.

00:09:12.183 --> 00:09:15.039
I saw drones flying in the sky.

00:09:15.039 --> 00:09:22.342
I could see our Marines protecting these places with heavy artillery, ready in case.

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:32.000
The Lord kept saying, 'Guerrilla warfare, guerrilla warfare.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:45.279
' I could hear people coming out of the jungles threatening these young men in the cartel: 'If you don't do what we tell you, we'll eliminate your whole family.

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:53.839
You fight for us or we will take out your grandma, your mama, and all your sisters and force them into slavery.

00:09:53.839 --> 00:09:56.160
' I saw these young men in white T-shirts.

00:10:00.845 --> 00:10:03.739
They didn't look like they had much.

00:10:05.690 --> 00:10:11.200
Some had longer hair, but they looked like they were being forced to fight.

00:10:11.520 --> 00:10:17.417
I saw them being given guns and going into jungle warfare.

00:10:17.417 --> 00:10:23.279
Some of these people, especially from Cuba, were very familiar with the terrain.

00:10:27.147 --> 00:10:35.794
I saw over ten thousand people trying to infiltrate to take the land and cause havoc for America in the days ahead.

00:10:36.206 --> 00:10:40.800
This was also concerning Colombia.

00:10:40.800 --> 00:10:43.079
I saw things coming for Colombia.

00:10:43.079 --> 00:10:52.491
I saw Claudia pacing back and forth in a room with old antique furniture.

00:10:53.029 --> 00:10:56.980
It was beautiful cherrywood furniture.

00:10:56.980 --> 00:11:02.650
It looked like something out of the Victorian era.

00:11:04.423 --> 00:11:06.831
It looked very Victorian where she was.

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:19.120
She was in a room and on the phone talking to the Colombian president?

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:27.138
I don't know who he was or what his title is, but she was talking to him.

00:11:27.138 --> 00:11:30.080
He acted cocky like he didn't care.

00:11:35.455 --> 00:11:35.807
She was pacing back and forth with nervous energy.

00:11:45.519 --> 00:11:45.750
I could see her in her room pacing back and forth, asking, 'What do we do?

00:11:45.750 --> 00:11:52.220
' She's afraid for her life because of the cartel that is backing her.

00:11:52.220 --> 00:12:02.720
At times she acted like she was scared for everything because of what's coming: a storm.

00:12:06.760 --> 00:12:08.480
I told you a major revival is about to hit Mexico.

00:12:18.784 --> 00:12:19.008
I saw liberation coming for the Mexican people, and for Colombia, Venezuela, and Cuba.

00:12:19.008 --> 00:12:23.413
A major revival is coming to South America.

00:12:41.690 --> 00:12:42.000
It's already, I believe, taking place in Brazil, but the Lord showed me a major revival coming in the days ahead for all of South America.

00:12:42.000 --> 00:13:10.970
But as I was seeing the head of state be cut, the drug distribution and oil revenue, this was about major business concerning backing the dollar and all the things coming for the dollar, trying to sustain life in America.

00:13:10.970 --> 00:13:14.856
This is what I thought was interesting.

00:13:14.856 --> 00:13:21.279
Remember I told you I saw the prime minister of Italy—the woman?

00:13:21.279 --> 00:13:40.212
She does not like the situation with Greenland, and the Lord warned us how many times about her standing up with Mark in Canada, England, Macron, Germany, Finland, and these nations.

00:13:42.429 --> 00:13:48.879
And I saw a major business deal coming about with the United States of America offering each person in Greenland a sum of money.

00:13:48.879 --> 00:13:51.069
It was over $20,000 per citizen.

00:14:11.028 --> 00:14:11.325
It was divided fifty-fifty.

00:14:13.210 --> 00:14:16.765
I saw a vote coming, but it was split fifty-fifty.

00:14:26.384 --> 00:14:27.008
A lot of the young people were excited about it; the elders weren't.

00:14:37.519 --> 00:14:38.119
I saw something with the fishing industry.

00:14:58.901 --> 00:14:59.563
The elders wanted to keep the way they've always lived, but it was about minerals and all these things.

00:15:10.640 --> 00:15:11.160
And I saw Trump say, 'I'm going to strongarm them.

00:15:11.160 --> 00:15:16.480
' This is where the vision stopped.

00:15:20.427 --> 00:15:25.394
I didn't see that they became a part of America, so I don't want to add to or take away from anything.

00:15:25.394 --> 00:15:41.769
But as I saw a shaking coming to Canada—specifically British Columbia—I saw they would secede from Canada in the days ahead and become a part of America.

00:15:41.769 --> 00:15:48.600
British Columbia would try to pull away from Canada because of financial trouble that's coming.

00:15:48.600 --> 00:15:57.120
I told you I saw Taiwan, and I keep seeing Taiwan.

00:15:57.120 --> 00:16:08.800
I saw an escalation of things where China was trying to devise a plan with their generals for taking Taiwan.

00:16:08.800 --> 00:16:17.533
When I see this dome of prayer, I heard the Lord say, 'You can delay the inevitable.

00:16:17.533 --> 00:16:20.755
' You can delay this through prayer.

00:16:25.920 --> 00:16:29.154
I saw a golden dome come up over Taiwan on all sides through prayer.

00:16:29.154 --> 00:16:39.389
But as I was interceding, the Lord said they have not taken their freedom from the communist regime of China seriously over the years.

00:16:39.389 --> 00:16:43.039
They've taken their freedoms for granted and haven't prayed enough.

00:16:43.039 --> 00:17:03.862
As I was looking into South Korea, the Lord said it will even be challenging in the days concerning South Korea, and a communist dragon will try to grab onto South Korea.

00:17:09.120 --> 00:17:10.987
But because there's more prayer root there, it will be held back.

00:17:21.180 --> 00:17:27.440
As long as my people in South Korea intercede and pray, it will hold back communism from their nation.

00:17:27.440 --> 00:17:41.429
As long as they humble themselves and pray, turning from their wicked ways, He said, 'Brandon, I will have a hedge of my protection over South Korea.

00:17:41.429 --> 00:17:44.920
' I saw it trying to infiltrate.

00:17:44.920 --> 00:18:01.279
It was a Chinese-looking spirit, like a snake or a dragon coming out of China into North Korea, trying to come over.

00:18:24.240 --> 00:18:24.480
It was a bad way of thinking through their government and their politics.

00:18:24.480 --> 00:18:28.549
He said it's trying to get a stronghold through their leaders.

00:18:28.549 --> 00:18:37.750
They don't have the right leaders.

00:18:44.187 --> 00:18:44.373
Pray for their leaders; it's an infiltration from China coming in through North Korea.

00:18:44.373 --> 00:18:50.347
It's a spirit that's trying to hook them, but they will be a major pillar in the end-time church.

00:18:50.347 --> 00:18:53.160
Revival will go out from there if they pray.

00:18:54.987 --> 00:19:06.280
But I saw Taiwan with this golden dome on all sides; if the people will pray.

00:19:26.587 --> 00:19:26.942
If they don't, they'll fall within three days.

00:19:28.364 --> 00:19:33.946
I saw they'll fight for one day, then into the second, but by the end of the second day, it will completely fold.

00:19:35.960 --> 00:19:41.429
I saw the Chinese government using weapons that have never been used before, similar to what America did to Venezuela.

00:19:41.429 --> 00:19:52.880
They have the same technological weaponry capabilities, maybe even better in some ways.

00:19:52.880 --> 00:20:05.017
I still believe America is top, but there were things that China had that even America didn't have—secret things—and they would use them as a flex.

00:20:05.017 --> 00:20:11.306
These people had artillery, but it was no match for what China would try to do.

00:20:11.306 --> 00:20:14.057
It fell in three days, just like that.

00:20:14.057 --> 00:20:22.239
When I see all these things in the spirit and the Lord warns me, I know we can pray.

00:20:22.239 --> 00:20:26.760
That's why the Lord said, 'Cover them in prayer.

00:20:26.760 --> 00:20:37.360
' I saw a dome of glory around them, and He said, 'You can hold it and delay the inevitable of what will come in the days ahead.

00:20:37.360 --> 00:20:38.731
' Delay it.

00:20:42.400 --> 00:20:56.159
But as I saw Trump say this right here—you can play it: 'It is a source of pride for him.

00:21:04.992 --> 00:21:05.168
He considers it to be a part of China, and that's up to him what he's going to be doing.

00:21:06.338 --> 00:21:12.097
But I've expressed to him that I would be very unhappy if he did that, and I don't think he'll do that.

00:21:17.609 --> 00:21:17.960
I hope he doesn't do that.

00:21:31.360 --> 00:21:31.591
So you don't think you've set a precedent?

00:21:34.507 --> 00:21:39.627
He may do it after we have a different president, but I don't think he's going to do it with me as president.

00:21:39.627 --> 00:21:45.611
Supposing you're Xi Jinping and you've watched the events of the past; you're probably impressed with it.

00:21:45.611 --> 00:21:48.766
' 'The special operators—he was impressed.

00:22:05.147 --> 00:22:11.993
You may also be thinking that if you're Xi, you could use the same logic to decapitate and control Taiwan, or why couldn't Putin use that same argument to grab the rest of Ukraine or go beyond into other former Soviet states?

00:22:11.993 --> 00:22:18.880
In other words, have you created a precedent that you may come to regret later on?

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:19.600
' 'No.

00:22:19.600 --> 00:22:21.653
Because this was a real threat.

00:22:21.653 --> 00:22:23.831
You didn't have people pouring into China.

00:22:23.831 --> 00:22:26.520
You didn't have drugs pouring into China.

00:22:26.520 --> 00:22:31.919
You didn't have the jails of Taiwan opened up and the people pouring into China.

00:22:31.919 --> 00:22:39.520
There aren't that many people in the jails, but you didn't have hundreds of thousands of people coming from jails and mental institutions.

00:22:41.424 --> 00:22:45.850
But Taiwan—she would tell you Taiwan's a threat to China, that it's a separatist operation.

00:22:45.850 --> 00:22:47.350
What's the source of Xi's pride for him?

00:22:47.350 --> 00:22:49.480
' So in his mind, it's already theirs.

00:22:52.580 --> 00:23:01.696
The way it sounded to me, if they take it, I hope he doesn't do it in my term, but even then, it didn't sound like he's going to resist it.

00:23:03.280 --> 00:23:08.240
So maybe he will, maybe he won't, I don't know.

00:23:08.240 --> 00:23:12.880
So it kind of went with what I've been seeing.

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:35.300
Number two was praying over what I saw about the government coming in, and I saw Russia come in and just take out Zelensky and their government and all the things that are escalating in Europe.

00:23:35.300 --> 00:23:45.320
So you've seen a lot of the shorts that my son has been making.

00:23:45.320 --> 00:23:51.151
He has been hard at work, hasn't he?

00:23:51.151 --> 00:23:55.600
Making shorts and making drawings.

00:23:55.600 --> 00:24:04.080
You know, everybody said, 'Brandon, can you comment on some of these things that you posted?

00:24:04.080 --> 00:24:11.966
' No, it's—we did it like The Economist.

00:24:29.191 --> 00:24:29.396
We were having fun putting on there.

00:24:29.396 --> 00:24:31.000
There's no explanation.

00:24:31.000 --> 00:24:36.907
I'm not here to interpret a vision of what I've seen.

00:24:36.907 --> 00:24:41.211
I put on what I saw.

00:24:41.211 --> 00:24:55.794
Now, The Economist doesn't interpret what they put on there and tell you, 'This is what we're trying to say.

00:24:55.794 --> 00:24:58.143
' You pray about it.

00:24:58.143 --> 00:25:03.626
You pray about every person that I put on there.

00:25:03.626 --> 00:25:11.413
I'm not saying the Lord didn't tell me to do that.

00:25:11.413 --> 00:25:20.297
He said, 'Be bold and put this on there and then walk away.

00:25:20.297 --> 00:25:28.543
' So that's what we did, and we're making a new one.

00:25:28.543 --> 00:25:33.360
It's going to be even better than this last one.

00:25:33.360 --> 00:25:36.400
Braden said, 'That was fun.

00:25:36.400 --> 00:25:37.240
I enjoyed that.

00:25:37.240 --> 00:25:40.308
Let's make another one.

00:25:40.308 --> 00:25:44.240
' So we're making another one.

00:25:52.250 --> 00:25:53.269
It will be even more detailed.

00:25:53.279 --> 00:26:05.386
The next one we work on is going to be a piece of work, but it's going to be an amazing art piece.

00:26:05.386 --> 00:26:07.406
I'm excited about it.

00:26:08.183 --> 00:26:19.580
I told him, 'We'll work on this for a couple of days, a week or so, whatever, and then we'll present it to the people, and they can look at it.

00:26:19.580 --> 00:26:35.289
' But it's all the things the Lord has shown me in visions, and we put it together and just present it to the people.

00:26:35.289 --> 00:26:37.617
So, pretty neat, I guess.

00:26:37.617 --> 00:26:39.440
So, was that it?

00:26:39.440 --> 00:26:41.093
No.

00:26:41.093 --> 00:26:43.595
Play this.

00:26:52.639 --> 00:26:52.853
Now this is interesting.

00:26:56.860 --> 00:26:57.120
This is the head of the NATO army, I guess.

00:26:57.120 --> 00:26:57.639
Yes.

00:26:57.639 --> 00:26:59.479
Can you play what he says?

00:26:59.479 --> 00:27:00.549
This is pretty interesting.

00:27:00.549 --> 00:27:07.519
Experience of the two nations' militaries, a deep commitment to the alliance, and a sense of urgency—and that sense of urgency is essential.

00:27:07.519 --> 00:27:17.840
When I look around the globe—Russia, China, Iran, North Korea, and others are increasing their collaboration and their cooperation as their interests align against us.

00:27:18.800 --> 00:27:20.903
We see this clearly in Ukraine.

00:27:20.903 --> 00:27:32.648
While President Trump pushes for a peaceful resolution to a horrible war, China continues to fund Putin's war machine.

00:27:32.648 --> 00:27:39.467
Iran continues to supply technology and weapons, and North Korean combat troops remain in Russia on Ukraine's border.

00:27:43.780 --> 00:27:50.820
And of course, there's a confluence between Russia, Iran, and Venezuela and their dark fleet of oil tankers that is helping to fund the war.

00:27:50.820 --> 00:27:55.540
In the Arctic and the High North, we see a similar trend.

00:27:55.540 --> 00:28:01.166
Russian and Chinese vessels are conducting more and more joint patrols.

00:28:01.166 --> 00:28:07.920
Chinese icebreakers and research vessels are in Arctic waters, and their research is not for peaceful purposes.

00:28:07.920 --> 00:28:11.600
It's to gain a military advantage.

00:28:11.600 --> 00:28:16.766
Russia, meanwhile, continues testing advanced capabilities in the Barents Sea.

00:28:16.766 --> 00:28:24.400
As new shipping routes emerge and new resources are discovered, the Arctic only grows in strategic importance.

00:28:29.543 --> 00:28:35.657
And all of this comes in the midst of an increasing hybrid threat: airspace violations, GPS and GNSS interference, and the shadow fleet in the Baltic Sea threatening underwater infrastructure.

00:28:45.572 --> 00:28:48.016
In short, the Arctic and Northern Europe by extension have become a frontline for strategic competition within NATO Allied Command Operations.

00:28:58.896 --> 00:28:59.120
The command that SACEUR oversees has taken steps to strengthen our deterrent posture, much of which is oriented in that northern region here.

00:29:01.190 --> 00:29:02.168
Just over a year ago, we established Baltic Sentinel, an activity.

00:29:02.168 --> 00:29:02.559
Yeah.

00:29:15.840 --> 00:29:16.920
And then Cuba, and then he had...

00:29:16.920 --> 00:29:18.800
what is it?

00:29:18.800 --> 00:29:19.600
Committee address.

00:29:19.600 --> 00:29:20.899
United States and Russia...

00:29:23.874 --> 00:29:24.240
and he posted something in Russian.

00:29:24.240 --> 00:29:24.987
Who did that?

00:29:24.987 --> 00:29:30.367
'United States is miscalculating today in retaliation to Iran.

00:29:30.367 --> 00:29:33.340
' I don't know.

00:29:33.340 --> 00:29:35.333
He made a post in Russian.

